Hey Ray,
What I did was buy a rebuildable front end and rebuilt it while driving.
Clara might have one cheap.  I bought spindles and steering box from
Wolfgang.  The spindles were a little over $200-220.  Link pin kits about
$75 I think, but mine is 67, forgot which year yours is.  I got the beam
blasted, then por'ed it.  New brake stuff was already there.  $2000 sounds
way high. I rebuilt mine for about $1000 including steering box, drag
link, tie rods, centerpin bushing, shocks, rebuilt exchange spindles from
Wolfgang.
John K.
